Title: Hell Money
Plot: The deaths of several Chinese men found to be missing vital internal organs that were removed prior to death leads Mulder and Scully to a deadly Chinatown lottery where men wager their body parts for a chance to win a cash jackpot.
GuestStars: B.D. Wong, Michael Yama, Lucy Liu, James Hong, Doug Abrahams, Stephen M.D. Chang, Donald Fong, Diana Ha, Paul Wong, Graham Shiels, Ed Hong-Louie
